<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>11064</hymn_number>
<title>qwmwạ nsbḥ klnạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qūmūạ nusabĩḥ̊ kulũnā
 lil̊kāhini ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 ạảs̊māw̉nā man̊qūsẖaẗuⁿ
 fī ṣad̊rihi ạlrãḥīm̊

[V2]
 qad̊ gẖasala bidamihi
 ạảẘzāranā hunā
 wah̊wa hunāka sẖāfiʿuⁿ
 ṭūla ạl̊maday̱ lanā

[V3]
 ại̹dẖ̊ jāza fī dẖāti ạlṭãrīq̊
 fī haẙyảẗi ạl̊basẖar̊
 yuʿīnu ḍaʿ̊fa sẖaʿ̊bihi
 wayad̊faʿu ạl̊kẖaṭar̊

[V4]
 yaqūlu lī hāảnadẖā
 ḥayuⁿ̃ lạảj̊lika
 ạảḥ̊bab̊tuka fadaẙtuka
 ạảr̊tẖī liḍaʿ̊fika

[V5]
 lạ sababa yaq̊diru ạản̊
 yukẖ̊mida ḥubã dẖāk̊
 māta hunā ʿanãạ kamā
 yaḥ̊yā lanā hunāk̊

[V6]
 fal̊nadẖ̊kuri ạl̊faḍ̊la ạl̊ʿaẓīm̊
 wal̊nasẖ̊du lạs̊mihi
 wal̊taʿ̊tarif̊ sẖifāhunā
 biʿuẓ̊mi ḥubĩhi</lyrics>
</song>